data.description: Cozy 3 bedroom home on corner lot in Crestwood School District. Home features updated kitchen cabinets, appliances, furnace (2018), and Hot Water Heater(2017). House has Chimney pipes if you would like to install wood burner or fire place as additional heat source. 8' Privacy wood fence around backyard with above ground heated pool and 16x14 Shed for yard tools. Bring your finishing touches to make this your perfect home!!
